ospital or other care unit that is the context of this service.</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ParticipationFunction.html#v3-ParticipationFunction-PCP\">PCP</a></td><td>Médecin traitant</td><td>The healthcare provider that holds primary responsibility for the overall care of a patient.</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
